## Complete Free Architecture

```
You (git push) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
                                                                         │
                                                            GitHub Actions (FREE)
                                                              │
                    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┤
                    │                                         │
                 ci.yml                            cd workflow (on main)
             (every push)                          (serve.py changes)
                    │                                         │
        ┌───────────┴──────────────┐                          │
        │                          │                    HF Spaces (FREE)
   SonarCloud (FREE)          Codecov (FREE)         ┌────────────────┐
   code quality                coverage               │  samos-api     │
                                                      │  FastAPI :7860 │
                                                      │  Dashboard     │
                                                      └───────┬────────┘
                                                              │
                                               ┌──────────────┴──────────────┐
                                          DagsHub (FREE)             Upstash Redis (FREE)
                                         MLflow tracking             MAB + Memory state
```

